shortDescription:
We offer for sale, in exclusive representation and without commission from the buyer, an apartment in the house (duplex), with a total area of 220 square meters on Jozsef Attila street no. 49 in the Andrei Muresanu neighborhood, Cluj-Napoca.

The apartment, part of a house with 2 apartments (duplex), is divided as follows:
- Mezzanine/Ground floor: garage 28 sqm, cellar 26 sqm;
- Upper ground floor: kitchen, living room 28 sqm, service toilet, pantry, hall, access to the garden;
- Floor: 2 rooms of 14 and 20 square meters, bathroom with glass, hall;
- Loft/Attic: open space 56 sq m, height over 3 m;
The two big assets of this property are, first of all, the area, only 1.8km from the center (16 min walk), located on a street with almost non-existent car traffic, set back from the main traffic arteries, which serves only the riversiders. Secondly, the first thing we notice when entering the house is the height of the ceilings (2.6m) and the large windows specific to interwar constructions.
The house was built on a 500 square meter plot at the end of the 70s on a concrete structure with 30cm brick masonry. Recently, the building was renovated and thermally insulated with a system based on 15cm polystyrene. The floors, including the one on the bridge as well as the stairs, are made of concrete. As for the interior finishes, we can say that they are "classic", but the solid wood parquet in very good condition stands out. The high attic (56 square meters) is prepared for the attic, resulting in at least one extra generous room.
Of course, the house benefits from all the utilities, and the heating is done by its own gas boiler. The electrical installation is based on copper and does not need to be replaced.
The legal situation is clear, payment by credit is also accepted.
Given the generous area as well as the location, this property lends itself to a family that values both the tranquility of everyday life and accessibility.
Please watch the presentation video, the virtual tour, and for additional information, do not hesitate to contact us.
